{"tid":2005517,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"殘酷現實揭示受教育程度決定社會階層","createTime":"2020-05-07T07:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T08:09:51.000Z","uid":85524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b86e6fc0afa75e998960709699316b297cd0e8e","tid":2005517,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T07:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮人註定一輩子受窮？富人註定一生位高權重？做富人或者做窮人，是靠雙手、靠自己還是社會資源分佈不均？香港江南四大家族之一的富豪田北辰參加了香港本地一檔叫做《窮富翁大作戰》的真人秀節目，按節目的要求體驗了一把時薪只有25港幣的環衛工的生活。這位畢業於哈佛大學管理系、身家不知多少個億的富豪不禁感嘆萬分地說：這個世界正在懲罰不讀書的人!<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/news/a34m946.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fnews%2Fa34m946.html&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdQ3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=057f4651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/news/a34m946.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2C2FBk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2C2FBk.png&h=191e8a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605a9f683ef100e4362f5313a76dd6623a43e735","tid":2005517,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在田北辰這期節目的末尾，他結束體驗生活，重新以富翁身份，面對鏡頭，反思了很多，這四句話，最讓人印象深刻：<br />\n<br />\n「沒有學歷、技術的人，為了活下去，不是住籠屋就是要工作到半夜，但對於他們，最重要事情是下一頓吃什麼，怎麼會有時間和精力去思考未來怎麼發展？」<br />\n<br />\n「來來去去都在死胡同！」<br />\n<br />\n「在強弱懸殊的情況下，只有弱者越弱，越來越慘」。&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/news/a34m946.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fnews%2Fa34m946.html&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdQ3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=057f4651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/news/a34m946.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3dc99406093be03129065cf51d061ec9e0fa99cb","tid":2005517,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠點睇"}